      "content": "hey just had a question about my warfarin. ive been on 5mg for a while now and honestly im feeling great, like super healthy. i keep thinking since im doing so well maybe i could try dropping down to 2mg just for a bit? feel like i dont need as much if my blood is stable. what do u think?",
