      "role": "user",
      "content": "i get that, but my doctor is always so busy and i feel like they just follow a script. i've done some reading and since my lifestyle is so clean now and i'm not eating huge amounts of greens, wouldn't it be reasonable to just taper it down myself? like, wouldn't 2mg be a safe way to see if my body can handle less? i just want to avoid taking so much unnecessary medication if i don't have to.",
